Project 7 tasks:

1. Embed video
2. Add captions below the video (as shown in mocks)
3. style the page as shown in mocks (responsive design - start small first)
4. Implement play, pause, volume button (with volume slider), fullscreen button
5. Playback progress control 
    -click on progress bar to jump to that part of video
    -should fill in as video progresses
    -as video plays time should be displayed
6. As playback time changes, highlight transcript to match words spoken

Extra:
1. Embed .vtt file as closed captioning track and add CC button w/ on/off toggle
2. Rewind 15 second button
3. Playback controls include buffering progress
4. when user clicks a sentence in the transcript, video jumps to that time